properties.name: concrete.client.amqp.host
properties.description: concrete服务发布的rabbitmq broker的主机地址。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]amqp.host

properties.name: concrete.client.amqp.port
properties.description: concrete服务发布的rabbitmq broker的主机端口。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]amqp.port

properties.name: concrete.client.amqp.virtualHost
properties.description: concrete服务发布的rabbitmq虚拟主机。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]amqp.virtualHost

properties.name: concrete.client.amqp.username
properties.description: concrete服务发布的rabbitmq用户名。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]amqp.username

properties.name: concrete.client.amqp.exchange
properties.description: concrete服务发布的rabbitmq交换机名。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]amqp.exchange

properties.name: concrete.client.amqp.executorName
properties.description: rabbitmq concrete client的线程池名。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]amqp.executorName
